(170, 1, '2024-12-17 03:27:19', '2024-12-17 02:27:19', 'Enhance your bathroom with this <strong>set of two vanity units</strong>, designed to combine <strong>modern style</strong> with optimal <strong>functionality</strong>. Perfect for families, couples, or shared spaces, these vanities offer generous storage solutions while maintaining a sleek and elegant look.\r\n<h3><strong>Key Features</strong>:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>Contemporary and Elegant Design</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Clean lines and a modern finish that seamlessly blend with any bathroom decor.</li>\r\n 	<li>Available in various finishes to match your style (glossy white, natural wood, matte gray).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>High-Quality Materials</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Durable MDF construction with a waterproof coating to resist moisture and daily wear.</li>\r\n 	<li>Premium ceramic sinks with a smooth, scratch-resistant surface that’s easy to clean.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Optimized Storage Space</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Each vanity features <strong>2 spacious soft-close drawers</strong> for organized storage of towels, toiletries, and bathroom essentials.</li>\r\n 	<li>Compact design while offering maximum storage, ideal for both small and large bathrooms.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Easy Installation</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Quick and straightforward assembly with a detailed, illustrated manual included.</li>\r\n 	<li>Compatible with standard plumbing systems for hassle-free installation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Perfect Dimensions and Flexibility</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dimensions per unit: <strong>31.5\" (W) x 17.7\" (D) x 23.6\" (H)</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Designed for dual use, ensuring comfort and convenience in shared spaces.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3><strong>Why Choose Our Vanity Units?</strong></h3>\r\n✔ <strong>Dual Functionality</strong>: Two separate units allow for simultaneous use, perfect for couples and families.\r\n✔ <strong>Modern Aesthetics</strong>: Minimalist design that enhances the brightness and harmony of your bathroom.\r\n✔ <strong>Long-Lasting Durability</strong>: Waterproof and easy-to-maintain materials ensure years of reliable use.\r\n✔ <strong>Space-Saving Solution</strong>: Intelligent storage that maximizes your available space without compromising style.\r\n\r\nTransform your bathroom with this <strong>set of two modern vanity units</strong> and enjoy a stylish, practical, and durable upgrade. Create a space where <strong>design meets comfort</strong> and simplify your daily routine with elegance.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"moz-extension://3acdd44b-f1a4-4683-9d99-1a5bed358715/js/app.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"moz-extension://3acdd44b-f1a4-4683-9d99-1a5bed358715/js/app.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>', 'Set of Two Modern Vanity Units', '<strong>Short Description</strong>:\r\nUpgrade your bathroom with this <strong>set of two modern vanity units</strong>, featuring a sleek design, premium ceramic sinks, and spacious soft-close drawers for optimal storage. Perfect for couples or families, these durable and stylish units combine functionality and elegance to transform any space. <strong>Easy to install</strong> and built to last, they’re the ideal addition to your contemporary bathroom.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"moz-extension://3acdd44b-f1a4-4683-9d99-1a5bed358715/js/app.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"moz-extension://3acdd44b-f1a4-4683-9d99-1a5bed358715/js/app.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'set-of-two-modern-vanity-units', '', '', '2024-12-17 03:27:58', '2024-12-17 02:27:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=170', 0, 'product', '', 0),
