(300, 1, '2024-12-17 04:42:01', '2024-12-17 03:42:01', '<strong>Product Title</strong>: <strong>FRIDHULT – Space-Saving Convertible Sofa</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Product Description</strong>:\r\nThe <strong>FRIDHULT</strong> convertible sofa is designed to make the most of your space without sacrificing comfort. With its compact size and efficient design, it transforms easily from a stylish sofa into a comfortable bed, making it perfect for smaller living areas. Whether you\'re hosting guests or need a quick sleeping solution, the <strong>FRIDHULT</strong> provides a practical and versatile option.\r\n\r\nIts sleek and modern appearance complements any decor, while its innovative mechanism ensures a seamless transition between sofa and bed. Ideal for apartments, studios, or guest rooms, this space-saving piece combines functionality with style to meet your everyday needs.\r\n<h3><strong>Key Features</strong>:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Space-Saving Design</strong>: Perfect for small spaces, offering maximum sleeping area without taking up extra room.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Easy Conversion</strong>: Quickly transforms from a sofa to a comfortable bed for convenience and comfort.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Versatile and Practical</strong>: Ideal for apartments, guest rooms, or any space where flexibility is needed.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Modern Aesthetic</strong>: Stylish design that complements various home decor styles.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe <strong>FRIDHULT</strong> convertible sofa is the perfect solution for maximizing space while providing comfort and functionality in smaller living areas.\r\n<h3><strong>Dimensions</strong>:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Sofa</strong>: 180 cm (W) x 85 cm (D)</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Bed</strong>: 180 cm (W) x 120 cm (L)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMaximize your space with the <strong>FRIDHULT</strong> convertible sofa, designed to offer both comfort and style in any room.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"moz-extension://3acdd44b-f1a4-4683-9d99-1a5bed358715/js/